The Master Alchemist's masterpiece is finally complete! Now you can access Onyx Final forms to use in battle. Soon you'll be able to collect fragments from Arena and the Heroic portal, as well as from special packs, to craft your own. These are more powerful versions of the Master Alchemist's favorite recipes and have access to their fusion power immediately!

But that's not all, the Master Alchemist has channelled the summer he spent strangely compelled to walk around capturing cute creatures into new alchemy combos! Look for these new combos in the new Hypno and Mon packs.
